long_class_specifier.description_string: Validation model for equipment enable logic

description.description_string: Compute array of enabled equipment – One small equipment, two large equally sized equipment
Compute array of enabled equipment – Equally sized units
Sort lead/lag alternate equipment with available equipment first
Sort lead/lag alternate equipment with available equipment first
Restore indices with respect to original vector u1AvaEqu

expression.simple_expression:
"

This model validates Buildings.Templates.Plants.Controls.StagingRotation.EquipmentEnable in a configuration with three equally sized units (component equEnaEqu) and in a configuration with one small unit and two large equally sized units (component equEnaOneTwo). Only the units of the same size are lead/lag alternated.

"
